18 §1281. Legislative finding
19 The Legislature of Louisiana finds that:
20 (1) There is a need to educate and inform the public as to the history and
21 background tradition of American law and Louisiana law.
22 (2) America and Louisiana's religious history plays an important role in the
23 background of our American law and Louisiana law.
24 (3) The role of religion in the constitutional history of both the United States
